title: Intel Makes Available NUC HD Graphics Driver 10.18.14.4294
text: Intel has rolled out a new HD graphics package compatible with its D34010WYB and D54250WYB NUC boards, as well as with the D34010WYK and D54250WYK NUC kits, namely version 10.18.14.4294. Since there is no changelog available for this release, I can only assume that it implements some improvements and bug fixes that enhance the devices’ performance.
